defaultIn order to widen its impact 
defaultbeyond the school setting
default, HIH is 
defaultalso designing and implementing community building events in the five locations in which it currently has schools. The 
defaultgoals of this Shared Communities Program are: to establish a wide range of Jewish-Arab community activities, from sports and culture to dialogue, study and responding to discriminatory events, and open the community activity to all who are interested.  In new locations the communities play a central role in helping open new schools. 
